# 0.1.0

Released: 2014-03-05

* add ruby update handling
* add $ruby_path configuration option to set static ruby path
* bug #2: check for the correct $ruby_install_path if $version_in_dir is false (thanks https://github.com/krakatoa)
* add CHANGELOG
